    "content": "What steps her Department is taking to tackle antisocial behaviour.",
    "speakername": "Jo Platt"
  },
  {
    "content": "Antisocial behaviour is blighting high streets and town centres right across the country, and our communities are paying the price. That is why this Government have made tackling it a top priority. We will restore neighbourhood policing, putting bobbies back on the beat in every corner of the country, and we will introduce new respect orders so that the police can get repeat offenders off our streets.",
